<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=11872" target="top">Medic's Pouch</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Very rare drop in Grieg's End, NO DROP, right click effect.<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16415" target="top">Anizok's Gauze Press</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Easily made by high skill Tinkers, Tradeable, right click effect.<br>
